1. SNS 
SNS stands for Simple Notification Service which is pub/sub model of exchanging messages between the Systems. It is called an Topic.
Topic = Whenever a message has been published to a topic, it would delivered to all the subscribers who has subscribed for that topic

Amazon SNS is an Fully managed Pub/Sub messaging and event-driven computing service, instead of we installing, configuring and managing an Messaging queue system on the on-premise environment, we can use Amazon SNS Topic


	